<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.10.10">
<l>taḷarviṉṟi yēyeṉṟu meṅkum paranta taṉimutaṉ ñāṉamoṉṟā</l>
<l>yaḷavuṭai yaimpulaṉ kaḷaṟi yāvakai yālaru vākiniṟkum</l>
<l>vaḷaroḷi yīcaṉai mūrttiyaip pūtaṅka ḷaintai yirucuṭaraik</l>
<l>kiḷaroḷi māyaṉaik kaṇṇaṉait tāḷpaṟṟi yāṉeṉṟuṅ kēṭilaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Holding on to the feet of Kṛṣṇa, the trickster of shining brightness,</l>
<l>the two lights, the five elements, the form, the lord of growing light,</l>
<l>who stands without form in ways unknown to the measuring five senses,</l>
<l>being one with knowledge, the solitary beginning that spread everywhere all the time without slackening,</l>
	<l>I am always without loss.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
